y is necessary for explaining the detected neutrino event\nIceCube-200107A.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Sep 2020 12:10:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 14 Nov 2020 12:54:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
